title: Austria Gross Household Saving Rate
description: Household Saving Rate in Austria increased to 17.21 percent in the second quarter of 2022 from 13.54 percent in the first quarter of 2022. Personal Savings in Austria averaged 14.95 percent from 1999 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 25.79 percent in the fourth quarter of 2020 and a record low of 5.28 percent in the third quarter of 2021. This page provides - Austria Gross Household Saving Rate - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: EUROSTAT
